<p>###How to make musical apps</p>

<ul>
  <li>Use <a href="http://puredata.info">Pure Data - http://puredata.info</a>.</li>
  <li><a href="http://charlesmartin.com.au/blog/2014/3/11/how-to-learn-pd">charlesmartin.com.au/blog/2014/3/11/how-to-learn-pd</a></li>
  <li><a href="http://github.com/cpmpercussion/ComputerMusicIntro">github.com/cpmpercussion/ComputerMusicIntro</a></li>
  <li>Get a Pd patch on a device quickly with <a href="http://www.mobmuplat.com">MobMuPlat: www.mobmuplat.com</a></li>
  <li>Use <a href="http://libpd.cc">libpd</a> to integrate a patch into an iOS or Android App.</li>
  <li>How-to Book: <a href="http://shop.oreilly.com/product/0636920022503.do">Brinkman, Peter. (2012). Making Musical Apps. Oâ€™Reilly Media.</a></li>
</ul>

